<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When 
1 - dojoConfig (parseOnLoad = false)
2 - Zend_Dojo_View_Helper_Dojo::$_useProgrammatic = true</p>

<p>On class Zend_Dojo_View_Helper_Dojo_Container method registerDijitLoader register js loader as OnLoad function and its appended to onload array in this case any other registered onLoad function will be executed before the dijit loader and all the widgets will not be available because the dojo parser didn't run yet.</p>

<p>Its should be unshifted to the onload array</p>

<p>array_unshift($this-&gt;_onLoadActions, $js);</p>

<p>Thanks</p>

